ackModal_main_2526740\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dcn1665702982352.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dcn1665702982352.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dcn1665702982352.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dcn1665702982352\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Session Mnemonics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">These mnemonics start and end a session. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__topic_d63827e1_d63828e1_d63829e1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1__entry__1\">\n Mnemonic\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1__entry__2\">\n Explanation\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">init</code>\n</p> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>} </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1__entry__2\">\n Initialize the device at the start of a session or when the display is refreshed.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">close</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5576e1_d5577e1_d5578e1__entry__2\">\n Return the device to non-Uniface state.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__section_akx_jwh_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852604e117\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Options Available with init and $DISPLAY_INIT</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Option </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">0 or setting not mentioned </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Causes all video attributes to be\n                        reinitialized at the end of a display. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">1 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Same as 0, but specifies the\n                        display as a stratus v102 display. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">2 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Same as 0, but specifies the\n                        display as an HP terminal. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">3 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Same as 0, but specifies the\n                        display as an HP terminal. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">4 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcn1665702982352__table_d5579e1_d5580e1_d5581e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Allows video attributes to be\n                        initialized just before the next display, instead of at the end of the\n                        previous display. Also, the initialization will not occur when the cursor is\n                        already on the correct position for the next display and the attributes are\n                        equal to the incoming video attributes. This provides better performance\n                        than the options 1 through 3. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__section_ndr_dxh_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d852604e196\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__p_d63836e1_d63837e1_d63838e1\">The assignment setting <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybr1665702721823.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybr1665702721823.html\" title=\"Change the init option in the device translation table.\">$DISPLAY_INIT</a> allows the <code class=\"ph codeph\">init</code> option to be changed without changing the entire\n            device translation table.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__p_d63839e1_d63840e1_d63841e1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example: Starting and ending a session</strong></p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dcn1665702982352__pre_hcj_gxh_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">BEGIN_DEVICE start device section\n^esc= init select alternate keypad\n^esc[1;24r close leave terminal in ’normal state’\n...\n^esc[%v;%hH cursor(1,1) cursor posit command; home is 1,1\nEND_DEVICE end device section\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526740\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526740\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Session Mnemonics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Session Mnemonics These mnemonics start and end a session. Mnemonic Explanation init { ( Option ) } Initialize the device at the start of a session or when the display is refreshed. close Return the device to non-Uniface state. Arguments Table 1. Options Available with init and $DISPLAY_INIT Option Description 0 or setting not mentioned Causes all video attributes to be reinitialized at the end of a display. 1 Same as 0, but specifies the display as a stratus v102 display. 2 Same as 0, but specifies the display as an HP terminal. 3 Same as 0, but specifies the display as an HP terminal. 4 Allows video attributes to be initialized just before the next display, instead of at the end of the previous display. Also, the initialization will not occur when the cursor is already on the correct position for the next display and the attributes are equal to the incoming video attributes. This provides better performance than the options 1 through 3. Description The assignment setting $DISPLAY_INIT allows the init option to be changed without changing the entire device translation table. Example: Starting and ending a session BEGIN_DEVICE start device section ^esc= init select alternate keypad ^esc[1;24r close leave terminal in ’normal state’ ... ^esc[%v;%hH cursor(1,1) cursor posit command; home is 1,1 END_DEVICE end device section Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}